B. Non-SCI journal

Williamson GR*, Stammers S, Tzeng WN, Shiao JC, Prokhorchik G, Lecomte-Finiger R (1999) Drifting and dreaming: is this how baby eels cross the Atlantic Oncean? Ocean Challenge 9(2): 40-45.


